{"tid":1640941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際戰線絕非無用! 美國宣佈禁止西藏新疆濫暴官員入境， 家屬都禁埋.","createTime":"2019-10-09T07:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T18:00:47.000Z","uid":134071,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"76a6513ce37b75556d52e8d805dff7b115a06905","tid":1640941,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"而家有人不斷吹國際戰線無用， 香港人要靠自己。<br />\n事實上，《香港人權與民主法案》一立， 一定會有人落鑊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/international/20191008/5E7XXWIP6FS672O6ZP2REWQMGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191008%2F5E7XXWIP6FS672O6ZP2REWQMGU%2F&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=72cea757\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191008%2F5E7XXWIP6FS672O6ZP2REWQMGU%2F&h=a66d68dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/international/20191008/5E7XXWIP6FS672O6ZP2REWQMGU/</a><br />\n<br />\n【傀儡有後果】壓制新疆中國官員及家屬遭制裁 被禁入境美國<br />\n7小時前<br />\n<br />\n美國宣佈制裁涉及壓制新疆的中國官員。圖為新疆維吾爾自治區一個集中營。<br />\n<br />\n 繼美國商務部以牽涉中國對新疆維吾爾壓迫為由，將8間中企與20個公安機構列入貿易黑名單後，美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）周二宣佈，將涉及壓制新疆的中國政府及共產黨官員，採取簽證限制措施。美國連串舉動令周四展開的新一輪中美貿易談判蒙上陰影。中國駐美大使館譴責美國「嚴重違反國際關係規範，干涉中國內政，損害中國利益」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>國務院宣佈，被認為負責對新疆維吾爾、哈薩克及其他少數穆斯林族群拘禁或進行人權侵犯，或在當中扮演共謀角色的中國政府及共產黨官員，將不獲簽發入境美國簽證。蓬佩奧表示，這些官員的家人也可能會面對同樣的簽證限制，包括有意到美國留學的官員子女。</strong><br />\n<br />\n國務院沒有公佈制裁名單，但43名跨黨派美國國會議員4月曾聯署去信國務卿蓬佩奧、財長姆欽和商務部長羅斯，呼籲制裁新疆自治區黨委書記陳全國等中共官員。"},{"pid":"9b951f6e885f4847871af91825f4a98c17f911c9","tid":1640941,"uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"美國商務部周一以牽涉中國對新疆維族打壓為由，將8家中企和20個公安機構列入貿易黑名單，其中包括4月曾被多位美國議員點名的中國監視設備製造商海康威視（Hikvision）及大華技術股份有限公司（Dahua Technology）。商務部長羅斯（Wilbur Ross）在聲明中強調：「美國政府及商業部無法也不會容忍在中國境內，少數族群遭受的殘酷壓迫。」"},{"pid":"68b5c8a0189ae5e06a841e1989adf855d5a32b28","tid":1640941,"uid":55130,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"比卡超:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312b2da80b5afa295e8598b2623c2889a879d5b9","tid":1640941,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68b5c8a0189ae5e06a841e1989adf855d5a32b28","tid":1640941,"uid":55130,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"比卡超:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ca1ab843ca108f848c75acb1eec419d30d5d6f","tid":1640941,"uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"312b2da80b5afa295e8598b2623c2889a879d5b9","tid":1640941,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68b5c8a0189ae5e06a841e1989adf855d5a32b28","tid":1640941,"uid":55130,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"比卡超:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"以今次case黎睇。<br />\n<br />\n比卡超家屬都可能入黑名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2076d33e127796672486eb37e05eccb813e58a8","tid":1640941,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28d5ab3e63dea826841328458a9b1bca809aa81","tid":1640941,"uid":193224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:4